data.description: GORGEOUS 3/2/3 CBS/BRICK HOME ON 1.26 ACRES WITH A 1536 SF TWO STORY GARAGE/WORKSHOP JUST SECONDS TO SHOPPING, I-95 AND TURNPIKE! COUNTRY LIVING ON A QUIET STREET WITH LOTS OF MATURE OAKS AND CITY WATER. THE LOT ALSO HAS ROAD ACCESS TO THE REAR, MAKING IT EASY TO PARK YOUR TOYS. THIS SOLID HOME HAS A METAL ROOF, TWO ZONE A/C, ONE BRAND NEW, BREAKFAST NOOK, LARGE LIVING ROOM WITH FIREPLACE AND VAULTED CEILING, FAMILY ROOM, DINING AREA, SPLIT PLAN, 7 X 14 LAUNDRY ROOM WITH TUB, NEWER WATER HEATER, HUGE ATTIC SPACE WITH BLOWN IN INSULATION, OVERSIZED ATTACHED TWO CAR GARAGE AND SO MUCH MORE. THE GARAGE/WORKSHOP IS IDEAL FOR BOAT STORAGE, MECHANIC OR WOODWORKING SHOP. UPSTAIRS IS PERFECT FOR A REC ROOM. THE LOT TO THE NORTH OWNED BY THE SAME FAMILY WILL REMAIN UNDEVELOPED FOR A LONG TIME.
